    "agendaChanges": "At the start of the meeting, Trustee Lawson moved to: (1) move Bond Program Consent Items (Section 10) to immediately after Approval of Agenda (Section 7), so the bond team could leave early; and (2) move Action Item 14.1 (Personnel Changes) to the consent calendar. Both changes were approved. As a result, the actual order was: Call to Order/Roll Call, Reconvene/Roll Call/Report Out on Closed Session, Welcome, Changes to Agenda, Approval of Agenda, Bond Program Consent Items (Section 10), Oral Communication (Section 8), School/Community Reports (Section 9), Discussion Items (Section 12), Consent Items (Section 13, now including 14.1 Personnel Changes), Action Item 14.2 (Resolution 35), Board and Superintendent Reports (Section 15), Information (Section 16), Correspondence (Section 17), Other Business (Section 18), Board Agenda Calendar (Section 19), Adjournment (Section 20). Section 11 (Bond Program Action Items) had no items and was skipped.",
